channel.title: Client.Java Wont Let Me Edit It
channel.description:
Im trying to edit my client.java for Jayscape v1. So i go to the commands, trying to add some more, lalala, go on, and none of them work! Half of the ones that are already there dont even work!!
I edited some names, like i changed Jayscape to my server name, that worked.
But like, half of the things wont change?? Im compiling correctly, and no errors are showing.. HELP!!
:confused:[br][size=1]Posted on: November 12, 2007, 02:43:07 PM[/size][hr]Also, how can i change my welcome screen to that faded screen?
Please be as SPECIFIC AS POSSIBLE
